Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:12.56,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布羅夫斯宅 臥室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔爾那傢伙還以為自己是去了安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是魔法騎士團50人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗王子大人 還當自己能贏可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這死色鬼黑幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許用那種下流的眼神看我姊姊 哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲還是這麼寵伊莉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要好好完成才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留那傢伙一條活命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對艾利斯家不利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算怎樣 黑幕是王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說席翁也是王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯家只為羅蘭德王效力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須確認席翁是否有資格成為王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對魔法騎士團50人 他能活著回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席翁不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他不是我 但他身上有著某種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與席翁相遇 最後救了他的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不覺得有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.92,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾國境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小組 開始準備 優先確保水源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上沒事的人搭帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別滑倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.85,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼亂七八糟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.77,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也幫忙搭下帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了 不干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琪法 說說萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的媽呀 肚子好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪法 萬年懶蟲說他不幫忙搭帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納只聽琪法的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 是不是對琪法做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看氣氛都有點不對勁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是在打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到心上人要是有個三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會很抑鬱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是出發前琪法對你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕萊納會死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推什麼推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去森林裡揀些柴火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帳篷怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你留守啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好今天是個大晴天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我先睡個午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 和我一起逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和席翁 和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻喜歡上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼啦 琪法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑這種時候開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我果然什麼都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 我也不希望你死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 萊納 我沒能保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·獻上契約之文·
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育沉睡於大氣中的光之精獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為逃得出我們艾斯塔布爾魔法騎士團的手掌心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自艾斯塔布爾國的敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鎧騎士不斷出現 襲擊我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鎧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾的魔法騎士團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往森林裡逃 重整隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席翁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…塔伊爾…那傢伙去打水…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還說跟著席翁就安全呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 琺爾 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席翁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有活著的夥伴 估計琪法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去救他們嗎 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來確實不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不逃我們就沒樂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·獻上契約之文·
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育沉睡於大氣中的惡意之精獸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個魔法加速了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·獻上契約之文·
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育沉睡於大氣中的惡意之精獸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你剛才的魔法是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的 我本來不想用啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！為什麼會用我們的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼持有者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙會招致災難的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我·獻上契約之文·釋放…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 別用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·獻上契約之文·
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放翱翔於天際的光之魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早點使出這種力量 大家也不用死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方就三個人倒好說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這種力量我都七年沒用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識到了有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼還真是少見 你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多來點恐懼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我開心開心 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有複寫眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你看樣好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物 看見了嗎 剩下的就只有那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘全部 都殺光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還能保持冷靜嗎 真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人會死 而你卻全無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都 隨心所欲地 解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠戮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至目之所及 皆化為灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎樣 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休得反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的分子會化作沙礫消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神 惡魔 勇者 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們稱我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·獻上契約之文·
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放覆蓋於天宙間的精靈之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在解析·解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「起源」為破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,430)}α
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一切皆不創造 不惠澤 不救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是抹消 粉碎為一片空白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潰滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩裂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…契約不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切…抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很危險 死…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  眼…要閉上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要閉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遮上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 喂 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.35,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德帝國 首都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德 皇家軍事特殊學院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖在學校被養著不就安生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪法 她還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在這蹲著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還是回到老地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年前 她姊姊因為間諜身份暴露被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下她和妹妹接受了我國的再教育
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為表對我國的忠心 我們讓妹妹留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說成人質不是更直白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人也真夠蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她妹妹早被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底就是個渣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但阿斯塔爾那小子還活著就等於白費功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目標是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們遭到了那些大人多少訓斥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了抱怨才叫我來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上還敢囂張 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 剛才那下還真有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話 你耍我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們耍我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是被人耍的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我翹掉之前 快把我關進牢裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王有旨 把你關進來的同時滿足你一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也可以說現在給我止血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:13.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德 拘留所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琪法 光顧著睡午覺成績會下降哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 為什麼萊納會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪說起好呢 麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢說麻煩的話揍飛你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打也別打頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛止住的血又要冒出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傷是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管我的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我得告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪法的妹妹已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似很久前就被殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼萊納會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來…原來你也是羅蘭德的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽別人告訴我妹妹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是從你的嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道還嘲笑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著我說喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我真是個蠢女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有隱約察覺到 妹妹可能已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我無能為力啊…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有戰爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼別人的領土 我完全不感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了嘛 午睡才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊爾 托尼 琺爾都白白送了命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定是有慾望的傢伙才會發起戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無慾無求的人卻會被捲進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那無慾無求的人該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然沒像席翁一樣想過改變國家之類的麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上有只用睡午覺 沒有人會受傷的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 琪法 我說了什麼奇怪的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 琪法 過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你被釋放 琪法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再恭喜我入獄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常完美 交易成立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令書上寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·琉特入獄 同時釋放琪法·諾爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和軍方直接交易的大惡人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼萊納要為我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了大家…害死了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人殺人 而是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭是怪物 國家也是怪物 慾望也是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也是…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但琪法是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡當午睡王國的國王統治一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪法在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道為什麼喜歡上萊納了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無慾無求到完全不需戒備 讓人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼想過 但我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為你的善良…與堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 你不是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢保證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 萊納 我會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且一定把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會窒息掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人「撓」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡嗎 聽說你自己蹲監獄來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 想探監費了我不少勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是關我的地方 從學校變成了監獄而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我會在北邊森林備好馬匹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做你會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙沒膽量讓戰鬥英雄蹲監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但會成為把你拉下英雄地位的口實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止都想辦法熬過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把你推下去的人 說不定挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 萊納 聽我一回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這次機會 我不敢保證今後還能來探視你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經失去了自信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴的犧牲 戰爭的爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我現在還未當上國王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的過失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算逃過了這次 今後又會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 你這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這悠閒地睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺能睡出什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡午覺…然後再思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了 席翁大人 差不多好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先被養著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想這裡包三餐帶午睡還是很給力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 席翁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了一切的我 已經沒什麼可猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早點使出這種力量 大家也不用死…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然受不了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:23:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要發起戰爭呢 想想都嫌麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄燈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天發生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始有很多事都不會發生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之從現在起多得是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩 努力 加油什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要睡著就什麼都不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明這樣就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:44.84,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·報告書

